Class Tickets

airvia.airvialtd.Tickets
public class Tickets extends Object
This class represents a ticket in the system, which is used to book flights for customers.

      public Tickets(Integer ticketID, String validityStatus, String purchaseDate, String paymentType, Float paymentTotal, Integer currencyID, Integer blankID, String refundStatus)
      Creates a new Ticket object with the given parameters.
      Parameters:
      ticketID - the ID of the ticket
      validityStatus - the validity status of the ticket
      purchaseDate - the purchase date of the ticket
      paymentType - the payment type of the ticket
      paymentTotal - the total payment amount of the ticket
      currencyID - the currency ID of the ticket
      blankID - the blank ID associated with the ticket
      refundStatus - the refund status of the ticket
